Description of the STIS Instrument

   STIS is one of the second generation instruments successfully installed
   on the Hubble Space Telescope (HST) during the STS-82 servicing mission
   in February 1997. Additional information about STIS is available at the
   Ball Aerospace STIS page (includes some pictures) and at the Space
   Telescope Science Institute STIS page.
